        public void insert(E elem,

      • removeMinRandom

        public E removeMinRandom()
        Find one element with minimum priority, and swap it to the root. This implementation chooses a path to one node of the induced subtree containing elements with minimum priority randomly, thus, this choice is not uniform. Other suggestions are highly welcome :)
